rward and at the moment I\'m not striving for an end goal but just enjoying the path, and am enjoying the idea of not knowing what this next year or what life has in store but I must say it feels pretty perfect right now.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Physically right now as I sit here with my basketball on the TV, Google playing some jammin\' music, all being controlled by my phone. The connectivity is insane. I have a different drinks mat for each drink and baconzitos are on sale.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":564} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://openatlashome.files.wordpress.com/2019/02/img_5798.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_5798\" class=\"wp-image-564\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>(1 point for each for those who can guess which drinks go on which mat. Answers will not be accepted from those who I have already shown.)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The weather has cooled down this week and the fan is on half speed. It\'s one of those moments when all senses are satisfied but now it seems to be maintaining longer.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I remember in an inebriated state one night in uni when I returned home and felt particularly good, the lights and music were a good level and it felt like 5 orbs aligned and joined in perfect harmony and it\'s beginning to feel like that again.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/1-04-2014/M1obvl.gif\" alt=\"Image result for stars align gif\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>(bonus point for whoever can guess which Disney film this is from?)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>(and another bonus point who can guess my fancy dress theme this carnaval?)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:par